ink target=\"_blank\">https://dnscrypt.info/public-servers</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sWt3n8p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsWt3n8p.png&h=aa874b7e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n完成晒setup後, 用winscp或者其他工具 download Apple device用嘅mobileconfig, 同埋wireguard嘅QR code就搞掂<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://computingforgeeks.com/setup-personal-ipsec-vpn-with-algo-vpn/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcomputingforgeeks.com%2Fsetup-personal-ipsec-vpn-with-algo-vpn%2F&d=cH2nQL%2B7gNVGRZzFZPB6VqCH8iT5eEApQhURqQe1KTk%3D&h=bbc2e7b6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://computingforgeeks.com/setup-personal-ipsec-vpn-with-algo-vpn/</a>"},{"pid":"d67af9ae41f350775bac06ce032ae63fa913500f","tid":1639520,"uid":48851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T06:49:00.000Z","msg":"好似幾難"},{"pid":"86e2d580a0254bdd98342f6c28c00c9efd57c9f8","tid":1639520,"uid":164582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ddc9213de799a9a0d6e91ac286a0c0e8c22d229c","tid":1639520,"uid":14476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T15:57:54.000Z","msg":"可唔可以講下同v2ray比較，速度各加密性"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T15:32:28.000Z","msg":"速度好難對比<br />\nv2ray 本身唔同setup 已經有唔同速度<br />\n<br />\n加密性嚟講<br />\n樓主講嘅Algo VPN 個底係IKEv2同WireGuard <br />\n係真正嘅VPN <br />\n有晒規範/Whitepaper <br />\n而v2ray 都有規定<br />\n但未算得到廣泛(外國)嘅review<br />\n<br />\n即使係咁唔代表v2ray 安全性差<br />\nv2ray 所用嘅vmess 加密<br />\n係用AES-128-GCM/Chacha20-Poly1305<br />\n其中Chacha20-Poly1305 <br />\nAlgo VPN 都嘅WireGuard 都有用到"},{"pid":"623a5e9808bbe76bf4302756b6419a21688d1a4d","tid":1639520,"uid":14476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"86e2d580a0254bdd98342f6c28c00c9efd57c9f8","tid":1639520,"uid":164582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ddc9213de799a9a0d6e91ac286a0c0e8c22d229c","tid":1639520,"uid":14476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T15:57:54.000Z","msg":"可唔可以講下同v2r